OL,3,CUK and Irish Governments condemn New
OL,4,CIRA-claimed attacks on police stations
OL,6,FThe UK and Irish Governments have
OL,7,Fcondemned New IRA-claimed attacks on
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland police stations.
OL,10,FIn a joint communique following the
OL,11,FBritish-Irish Intergovernmental
OL,12,FConference took place at Hillsborough
OL,13,FCastle, the Governments welcomed
OL,14,F"excellent ongoing cooperation"
OL,15,Fbetween the PSNI and An Garda Siochana
OL,16,Fin "tackling terrorism, paramilitarism
OL,17,Fand associated criminality".
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@_O]xD@DOUyD@[O]
