OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1777662668
OL,3,CUK and Irish Governments condemn New
OL,4,CIRA-claimed attacks on police stations
OL,6,FThe condemnation came as the PSNI said
OL,7,Fdetectives investigating the attack on
OL,8,FSaturday Dunmurry Police Station have
OL,9,Fbeen granted an additional 36 hours by
OL,10,Fthe courts to question a 66-year-old
OL,11,Fman.
OL,13,FThe man was arrested on Tuesday under
OL,14,Fthe Terrorism Act, and taken to
OL,15,FMusgrave Serious Crime Suite for
OL,16,Fquestioning.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
