CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1777662668
OL,3,CUK and Irish Governments condemn New
OL,4,CIRA-claimed attacks on police stations
OL,6,FThe governments also discussed
OL,7,Fprogress in implementing the Joint
OL,8,FFramework on legacy issues in Northern
OL,9,FIreland while also discussing
OL,10,F"individual legacy cases" and the
OL,11,Freview of the Independent Commission
OL,12,Ffor Reconciliation & Information
OL,13,FRecovery.
OL,15,FThe UK Government was represented by
OL,16,Fthe Secretary of State for Northern
OL,17,FIreland Hilary Benn and the
OL,18,FParliamentary Under-Secretary of State
OL,19,Ffor Northern Ireland Matthew Patrick.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@YO]
