OL,3,CUK and Irish Governments condemn New
OL,4,CIRA-claimed attacks on police stations
OL,6,FThe government provided an update on
OL,7,F"the ongoing efforts to support the
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland Executive with public
OL,9,Fservice transformation and their
OL,10,Fbudget".
OL,12,FThe Government of Ireland was
OL,13,Frepresented by the Minister for
OL,14,FForeign Affairs and Trade and Minister
OL,15,Ffor Defence, Helen McEntee, and the
OL,16,FMinister for Justice, Home Affairs and
OL,17,FMigration, Jim O'Callaghan.
